==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: headword
<hw>headword</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a word that is
qualified by a modifier.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a word placed at the beginning of a line, paragraph,
or short article (as in a dictionary or encyclopedia entry); the word
which forms the title of an entry in a dictionary.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Headwork</ent>⟦br⟧
